				},
				"string" : "{{gtPackage:Gt4Cloudflare}} is a GT client for the [Cloudflare Browser Rendering REST API](https://developers.cloudflare.com/browser-rendering/rest-api/). This page walks through setup, each endpoint, and tips for working with results in the GT inspector."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
