				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# 1. Setup\n\nYou need two things:\n1. A **Cloudflare API token** with \"Browser Rendering - Edit\" permission ([create one here](https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens))\n2. Your **Account ID** (visible on the Cloudflare dashboard sidebar)\n\nSave your API token to `~/.secrets/cloudflare-api-key.txt`, then create a client. Inspect the client to see the **Configuration**, **Endpoints**, and **Calls** views."
			},
