				},
				"string" : "# 3. Scraping (`/scrape`)\n\nExtract specific elements using CSS selectors. Each match returns text, HTML, attributes, and dimensions. Inspect the result to drill into individual {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareScrapeElement}} objects."
