					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# 4. AI Data Extraction (`/json`)\n\nUses an LLM (Llama 3.3 70B by default) to extract structured data. You can guide it with a natural language **prompt**, a JSON **schema**, or both. Adding a schema makes results more reliable."
