				"code" : "\"With a JSON schema for more reliable results\"\nclient jsonFromUrl: 'https://example.com'\n\tresponseFormat: {\n\t\t'type' -> 'object'.\n\t\t'properties' -> {\n\t\t\t'title' -> { 'type' -> 'string' } asDictionary.\n\t\t\t'links' -> {\n\t\t\t\t'type' -> 'array'.\n\t\t\t\t'items' -> {\n\t\t\t\t\t'type' -> 'object'.\n\t\t\t\t\t'properties' -> {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t'text' -> { 'type' -> 'string' } asDictionary.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t'href' -> { 'type' -> 'string' } asDictionary\n\t\t\t\t\t} asDictionary\n\t\t\t\t} asDictionary\n\t\t\t} asDictionary\n\t\t} asDictionary\n\t} asDictionary."
