				"string" : "# 6. Crawling (`/crawl`)\n\nStart an **async** crawl that follows links from a starting URL. The API returns a job ID immediately — poll with {{gtMethod:Gt4CloudflareClient>>#getCrawl:}} or use the **Refresh** action button on the {{gtClass:Gt4CloudflareCrawlJob}} inspector."
