				"string" : "# 9. Markdown Conversion (`/ai/tomarkdown`)\n\nConvert files (PDF, images, HTML, Word, Excel, and more) to Markdown using Cloudflare Workers AI. Your API token needs **Workers AI - Read** permission.\n\nSubmit one or more local files and get back structured markdown with metadata and token counts. Inspect the result to see each file's converted content."
