				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "# Tips\n\n- **Rate limits**: The free plan allows 10 minutes of browser time per day. If you hit rate limits, wait a few seconds between calls.\n- **Options**: Every endpoint method has an `options:` variant accepting a dictionary with extra parameters like `gotoOptions`, `viewport`, `cookies`, `userAgent`, `authenticate`, etc.\n- **Request history**: Inspect the client to see the **Calls** view — every request/response pair is recorded for debugging.\n- **Error handling**: API errors (rate limits, invalid params) are raised as Smalltalk `Error` exceptions with the Cloudflare error message."
			},
